WEBVTT

00:06:02.287 --> 00:06:03.438
[Sauti ni kumbukumbu.]

00:06:03.462 --> 00:06:05.625
Na siyo tu kuhusu sauti ya gari.

00:06:06.448 --> 00:06:09.423
Ni kumbukumbu ya baba yangu
akirudi nyumbani.

00:06:11.737 --> 00:06:13.274
[Sauti inavutia.]

00:06:13.298 --> 00:06:18.949
Na sauti ina nguvu ya kutengeneza
maajabu yasiyotegemewa,

00:06:18.973 --> 00:06:20.400
ambayo huvutia.

00:06:22.004 --> 00:06:23.171
Na kwa ujumla,

00:06:23.195 --> 00:06:24.670
[sauti ni binadamu wa ajabu.]

00:06:24.694 --> 00:06:26.694
sauti huenda zaidi ya hali ya kibinadamu,

00:06:26.718 --> 00:06:29.361
kwa sababu inaturuhusu sisi kujongea.